flowchart LR
    GH[GitHub Issues<br/>label: agent-task]

    subgraph Orchestrator["Foundry Orchestrator (FSM)"]
        direction LR
        FETCH[Fetch] --> CONTEXT[Context]
        CONTEXT --> PLAN[Plan]
        PLAN --> IMPLEMENT[Implement]
        IMPLEMENT --> VERIFY[Verify]
        VERIFY -->|fail, ×3| IMPLEMENT
        VERIFY -->|pass| PR[PR]
    end

    DB[(SQLite<br/>tasks + stage logs)]
    WT[git worktree<br/>/tmp/&lt;task-id&gt;/]
    AGENT[Coding Agent<br/>Aider + LLM]
    OUT[GitHub PR<br/>gh pr create]

    GH -->|gh issue list| FETCH
    Orchestrator <-->|persist after each stage| DB
    IMPLEMENT --> WT
    WT <--> AGENT
    PR -->|commit / push| OUT
